quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  100,10,"And all what lies in the breasts is opened –"
  100,11,"On that day their Lord surely knows all about them!"
  101,1,"The event that terrifies the hearts!"
  101,2,"What is the event that terrifies the hearts?"
  101,3,"And what have you understood, what the event that terrifies the hearts is!"
  101,4,"The day when men will be like scattered moths."
  101,5,"And mountains will be like flying wool."
  101,6,"So for one whose scales prove heavy,"
  101,7,"He is therefore in the desired bliss."
  101,8,"And for one whose scales prove light,"
  101,9,"He is in the lap of one that abases."
  101,10,"And what have you understood, what the one that abases is!"
  101,11,"A flaming fire!"
  102,1,"The craving for excess wealth kept you people neglectful."
  102,2,"Until you confronted the graves."
  102,3,"Yes certainly, you will soon realise!"
  102,4,"Again, yes certainly, you will soon realise!"
  102,5,"Yes certainly, if you had believed with certainty, you would not have craved for wealth."
  102,6,"Indeed you will see hell."
  102,7,"Again, indeed you will see it with certainty."
  102,8,"Then, on that day, you will surely be questioned regarding the favours."
